ACnh-H%E1%BB%93-Nam-th%C3%A2n-h%E1%BB%AFu/poem-maRxAMOCboIbSdvxXl781Q">Phong tật chu trung phục chẩm thư hoài tam thập lục vận, phụng trình Hồ Nam thân hữu - 風疾舟中伏枕書懷三十六韻，奉呈湖南親友</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Linh-V%E1%BA%ADn/Thu-H%E1%BB%93-h%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-jxn87ZZRFzwNL0Dv_GL43Q">Thu Hồ hành kỳ 1 - 秋胡行其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Linh-V%E1%BA%ADn/author-7k3dwdcuJKTWbJGjPLm2kg">Tạ Linh Vận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BB%AD-Hy-Nhan/Tr%E1%BA%A3m-x%C3%A0-ki%E1%BA%BFm-ph%C3%BA/poem-4mnvnyA6k6RfA2JMT5OVyQ">Trảm xà kiếm phú - 斬蛇劍賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BB%AD-Hy-Nhan/author-_3sTvaRn7XDoRGq_884L9Q">Sử Hy Nhan</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/T%E1%BB%A9c-nh%E1%BA%ADt-Ti%E1%BB%83u-uy%E1%BB%83n-th%C3%AD-xu%C3%A2n-y/poem-mw0WX0k6V8PxDqhD4p0n1g">Tức nhật (Tiểu uyển thí xuân y) - 即日（小苑試春衣）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/V%C3%A3n-xu%C3%A2n-II/poem-_9Fa164ocZLdCK48vdXPmA">Vãn xuân (II) - 晚春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/author-mhAlF-W1JHQDMsH_S0aV3Q">Hà Như</a>)<br></div>	</div>
